Package gov.sandia.geotess.examples.customdata

Class GridPointData

java.lang.Object
gov.sandia.geotess.Data
gov.sandia.geotess.DataCustom
gov.sandia.geotess.examples.customdata.GridPointData
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.Map<java.lang.String,​StationData>
public class GridPointData
extends DataCustom
implements java.util.Map<java.lang.String,​StationData>
GridPointData manages the information associated with a single point in a GeoTessModel. GridPointData has information about GeoAttributes at a bunch of stations and phases. It is stored in a map station -> phase -> GeoAttributes -> value.
Author:
sandy
